      "explanationEn": "Used with verbs or adjectives to connect two actions or states. It functions like 'and'.",
      "examples": [
        {
          "ko": "인터넷으로 뉴스를 보고 음악을 듣습니다.",
          "bn": "আমি ইন্টারনেটে খবর দেখি এবং গান শুনি।",
          "en": "I watch news and listen to music on the internet."
        },
        {
          "ko": "이 스마트폰은 싸고 좋습니다.",
          "bn": "এই স্মার্টফোনটি সস্তা এবং ভালো।",
          "en": "This smartphone is cheap and good."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "pattern": "-(으)ㄹ 수 있다/없다",
      "titleBn": "পারা / না পারা",
